27
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 27=

28
00:01:51,580 --> 00:01:53,350
Your Highness,
when you go hunting next time,

29
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:54,590
be more careful.

30
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:57,150
Don't get scratched by branches again.

31
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,080
You are Da'an's symbol of good luck.

32
00:02:29,470 --> 00:02:30,590
I don't want your brilliance

33
