to be overshadowed by others.

34
00:02:32,130 --> 00:02:33,030
I understand.

35
00:02:33,030 --> 00:02:34,750
I won't let you down, Mother.

36
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:36,420
I only ask that
you look after your health

37
00:02:36,470 --> 00:02:37,750
and always stay by my side.

38
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,910
You belong to me.

39
00:02:52,430 --> 00:02:53,870
Don't ever leave me.

40
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,840
Your Highness, you're injured.

41
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,520
You need proper rest.

42
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,310
I'll take my leave.

43
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:20,550
Don't go.

44
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,190
Stay with me.

45
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,800
Your Highness,
your noble body is wounded.

46
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,560
You should rest properly.

47
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,640
I'll stay

48
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,840
by your side.

49
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,710
I demand you pledge

50
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,520
that you never leave my sight.

51
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:08,710
Will you accept?

52
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:15,030
Am I a caged bird?

53
00:04:18,870 --> 00:04:20,000
I dare not promise

54
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,830
what you wish.

55
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:37,870
I admire

56
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:39,880
your blunt honesty.

57
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,560
Rest well, Your Highness.

58
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:06,900
(Wei Residence)

59
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:11,910
Madam,

60
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,480
I have a family business to attend to.

61
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,040
I'd like to take a leave

62
00:05:16,270 --> 00:05:17,720
to return home and settle matters.

63
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:22,880
Nanny Lyu,

64
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:24,630
thank you for helping me.

65
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,800
You've been working hard these days.

66
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:29,420
I'll have the accounts office
prepare some silver for you.

67
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,630
Rest well

68
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:32,270
when you return home.

69
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:34,510
Thank you, Madam.

70
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,510
I've been investigating
the Wei Family.

71
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,120
Servants revealed

72
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,680
that Wei Xian had several concubines.

73
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,600
All of them died mysteriously.

74
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:44,680
Their bodies

75
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:45,680
were buried in this courtyard.

76
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:53,960
There is a discovery here!

77
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,680
These dead concubines

78
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:10,480
may be connected to Wei Xian's death.

79
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:11,990
Find a coroner for them.

80
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,550
In addition,
investigate their backgrounds

81
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,270
for clues.

82
00:06:17,510 --> 00:06:18,430
Another body here!

83
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:25,580
(Siyi Pavilion)

84
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,310
This is a Wei Family secret.

85
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:29,680
Truthfully,

86
00:06:30,310 --> 00:06:32,360
years ago, I gave birth to a child

87
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,800
who died soon after.

88
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,870
I always thought it was an illness.

89
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:39,950
Wasn't it?

90
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,390
After that,
I never had any more children.

91
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,360
Wei Xian took other concubines.

92
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:48,870
Not only did their children die,

93
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,390
but the women themselves
died mysteriously.

94
00:06:52,260 --> 00:06:54,310
(Siyi Pavilion)
Once or twice it could be explained.

95
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,800
But every time?

96
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:57,000
It's indeed strange.

97
00:06:57,830 --> 00:06:58,670
Half a year ago,

98
00:06:58,950 --> 00:07:00,600
his latest Concubine Huang

99
00:07:00,950 --> 00:07:02,120
gave birth to a baby.

100
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,720
I was concerned,

101
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:05,160
so I went to see her,

102
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:06,760
only to discover

103
00:07:06,950 --> 00:07:08,120
what Concubine Huang bore

104
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:09,360
was a freak.

105
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,680
The child died

106
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:11,670
immediately.

107
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,920
Wei Xian went mad.

108
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,950
He killed Concubine Huang by mistake

109
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:17,600
and almost killed me.

110
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:20,270
Luckily, he found his sense
at the last moment.

111
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,600
Since then,

112
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,040
his control over me

113
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:24,720
got tighter.

114
00:07:26,390 --> 00:07:27,240
So

115
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,680
those former concubines

116
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,830
all may have died at Wei Xian's hand.

117
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,870
Wei Xian must have had a secret illness.

118
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,040
All his children

119
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,240
were born deformed.

120
00:07:37,630 --> 00:07:38,870
To hide the truth,

121
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,830
he killed almost everyone who knew.

122
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:43,870
That's why I couldn't take it anymore

123
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:45,920
and decided to leave him.

124
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:48,160
So you orchestrated the haunting

125
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,040
not only to escape abuse,

126
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:52,000
but also to escape this murderer.

127
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,000
At first,

128
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,160
I didn't know what to do.

129
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:58,590
Nanny Lyu

130
00:07:58,800 --> 00:07:59,950
took pity on me

131
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,190
and suggested

132
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,070
the haunting plan.

133
00:08:03,200 --> 00:08:04,080
Could Wei Xian's death

134
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,480
be related

135
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,750
to the deaths of those concubines?

136
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:13,860
(Siyi Pavilion)

137
00:08:14,410 --> 00:08:15,870
(Favourable Climate)
According to Madam Wei,

138
00:08:15,890 --> 00:08:16,750
those concubines

139
00:08:16,750 --> 00:08:18,120
died one by one by Wei Xian's hand.

140
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,190
He would appease their families.

141
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:21,630
Investigating this angle

142
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,630
might provide clues.

143
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:25,160
Which concubine's family
are you looking for?

144
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,630
Concubine Huang died half a year ago.

145
00:08:28,090 --> 00:08:29,000
Her father Huang Laosi

146
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,070
runs a spice drink shop.

147
00:08:30,070 --> 00:08:32,660
(Huang's Spice Drinks Shop)

148
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,170
Why is no one here in broad daylight?

149
00:08:40,060 --> 00:08:44,140
(Huang's Spice Drinks Shop)

150
00:08:51,390 --> 00:08:52,390
Ask across the street.

151
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:54,910
Take care, customers.

152
00:08:54,910 --> 00:08:55,750
Come back again.

153
00:09:00,870 --> 00:09:01,710
Lady,

154
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:03,870
your perilla drink is excellent.

155
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,270
Worthy of an old-established shop.

156
00:09:05,510 --> 00:09:06,390
This is my husband's

157
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:07,400
ancestral business.

158
00:09:07,400 --> 00:09:08,420
This shop has been in operation

159
00:09:08,420 --> 00:09:09,390
for over a decade.

160
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:10,720
It's really

161
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,720
fresh and tasty,

162
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,000
unlike the shop opposite.

163
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,480
The opposite?

164
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,630
You mean Huang's Spice Drinks?

165
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:20,030
The owner is dishonest.

166
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:21,360
My mother bought two jars

167
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,630
the other day.

168
00:09:22,690 --> 00:09:23,630
She opened them at home.

169
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:24,790
And the liquid stank!

170
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:25,750
It made her furious.

171
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:26,720
How old was the stock?

172
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:27,600
They were still selling it.

173
00:09:28,030 --> 00:09:29,480
How can they compare?

174
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:31,240
We have ancestral recipes.

175
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:33,080
This Huang Laosi

176
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,030
is a man
who pawned his wife and daughter.

177
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,180
What skills could he have?

178
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,320
Huang Laosi

179
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:39,270
is so despicable?

180
00:09:39,390 --> 00:09:40,230
Absolutely.

181
00:09:40,390 --> 00:09:41,960
In his youth,

182
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:43,840
he was a thorough ruffian

183
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,440
and lived off his parents.

184
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:47,440
After they died, he fell

185
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,720
into drinking and gambling.

186
00:09:49,100 --> 00:09:50,350
He pawned his wife and daughter.

187
00:09:50,350 --> 00:09:51,200
Completely evil deeds.

188
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,720
He's in a bestial manner.

189
00:09:53,900 --> 00:09:55,420
I only felt sorry
for the mother and daughter.

190
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,870
Where is Huang Laosi now?

191
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,440
Right next door.

192
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:02,280
You can see him
when you go across the alley.

193
00:10:06,180 --> 00:10:11,260
(Liu's Spice Drinks Shop)

194
00:10:15,060 --> 00:10:20,860
(Huang's Spice Drinks Shop)

195
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:26,670
I've definitely seen

196
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:28,120
