197
00:10:32,300 --> 00:10:33,790
Nanny Lyu,
are you making handicrafts again?

198
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,480
This knot is beautiful.

199
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:39,390
This method is strong and pretty.

200
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:41,080
I used to tie my daughter's...

201
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:47,630
What do you need?

202
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,120
Madam summons you.

203
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,470
Let's go.

204
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,750
Now I remember!

205
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:07,840
I've seen this style
at the Wei Residence.

206
00:11:08,180 --> 00:11:09,120
It was Nanny Lyu who tied it.

207
00:11:10,050 --> 00:11:11,540
(Huang's Spice Drinks Shop)
As the lady said,

208
00:11:11,910 --> 00:11:13,790
Huang Laosi's former wife

209
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,480
was Huang Xingzhi's biological mother.

210
00:11:17,460 --> 00:11:18,390
(Wei Residence)

211
00:11:18,390 --> 00:11:19,790
Nanny Lyu asking for leave now

212
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:21,230
is suspicious.

213
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:22,960
Could she be

214
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,320
fleeing guilt?

215
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:26,440
Not necessarily fleeing.

216
00:11:27,100 --> 00:11:28,540
If she is seeking revenge
in the Wei Family

217
00:11:28,540 --> 00:11:29,350
for her daughter,

218
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:30,750
she has

219
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:31,600
many enemies.

220
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:33,870
I've checked.

221
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:35,790
Concubine Huang who died half a year ago

222
00:11:35,790 --> 00:11:37,440
was pawned by her father.

223
00:11:37,790 --> 00:11:38,670
What's more,

224
00:11:38,910 --> 00:11:39,750
that villain

225
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,960
even pawned his own wife.

226
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,440
If

227
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,600
Nanny Lyu is the mother
of Concubine Huang

228
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:50,960
and the wife

229
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,030
Huang Laosi pawned...

230
00:11:54,630 --> 00:11:55,470
Let's go.

231
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:00,200
I need your confession now.

232
00:12:01,380 --> 00:12:02,540
(Huang Laosi)

233
00:12:04,020 --> 00:12:05,080
She really stabbed him.

234
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:06,440
Say it now!

235
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,160
I'll say!

236
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,080
I was wrong!

237
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,960
I shouldn't have drunk

238
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:15,510
and abused you and Xingzhi.

239
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:16,790
I shouldn't have

240
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:18,200
gambled addictively

241
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,510
and pawned you to pay off debts.

242
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:21,720
I shouldn't be a human.

243
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,910
I'm a beast!

244
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:24,480
Please forgive me,

245
00:12:24,720 --> 00:12:26,000
Chunlian!

246
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,550
Please consider our marital bonds.

247
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,480
How dare you mention marital bonds?

248
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:36,270
Ruining me was enough,

249
00:12:36,720 --> 00:12:37,600
why condemn

250
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,510
our daughter to hell?

251
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:40,870
I didn't.

252
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:41,840
Say it,

253
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,600
what did you do to Xingzhi?

254
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:47,080
What have I done?

255
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:48,670
I never meant to

256
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,910
make her suffer.

257
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:53,120
Although I was greedy
for the betrothal gifts,

258
00:12:53,120 --> 00:12:55,030
I sent her off as Wei's concubine.

259
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:58,600
But the Wei Family is very wealthy.

260
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:00,080
Even as a concubine,

261
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,910
she'd live comfortably!

262
00:13:03,270 --> 00:13:04,270
Comfortable?

263
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,840
Within a year with Wei,

264
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,790
she died.

265
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,120
I did my research.

266
00:13:14,870 --> 00:13:15,750
You knew

267
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:18,390
she died there suspiciously.

268
00:13:19,150 --> 00:13:21,670
Yet you took Wei Xian's silver

269
00:13:22,720 --> 00:13:23,630
and covered up

270
00:13:23,630 --> 00:13:25,510
our daughter's death.

271
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,600
